{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.get()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/get","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>get()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\"><code>getAll()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die <code><strong>get()</strong></code> Methode der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> Schnittstelle gibt die den ersten Wert, der dem gegebenen Schlüssel zugeordnet ist, aus dem <code>FormData</code> Objekt zurück. Wenn mehrere Werte zu erwarten sind und diese alle verwendet werden sollen, sollte stattdeessen die Methode <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll\" title=\"getAll()\"><code>getAll()</code></a> verwendet werden.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong><font>Hinweis</font></strong>: Diese Methode ist in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a> verfügbar.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">formData.get(name);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append_parameters","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>, der den Namen des abzurufenden Schlüssels repräsentiert.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormDataEntryValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, der den Wert enthält.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Example","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die folgende Zeile erzeugt ein leeres <code>FormData</code> Objekt:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Wenn man zwei Werte als <code>benutzername</code> mit <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>FormData.append</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> hinzufügt:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'benutzername'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Chris'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'benutzername'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Bob'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Der folgende Aufruf der <code>get()</code> Funktion liefert dann nur den zuerst hinzugefügten Wert für <code>benutzername</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'benutzername'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Gibt \"Chris\" zurück</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-get\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'get()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browserkompatibilität","title":"Browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span>Grundlegende Unterstützung</span></span></td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2015-06-30.\">39.0</a> (39.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Verfügbar in web workers</td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/39\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2015-06-30.\">39.0</a> (39.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><span class=\"short_text\" id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span>Grundlegende Unterstützung</span></span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Verfügbar in web workers</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>50.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\" title=\"Using XMLHttpRequest\">Using XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\" title=\"DOM/XMLHttpRequest/FormData/Using_FormData_objects\">Using FormData objects</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Example","id":"example"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},